item.title: Migrating from Google Workspaces to iCloud+
item.description: Google recently accounced that it was getting rid of the legacy free tier for Google Apps/Workspace accounts, something I've used for 10+ years, and I don't care for that. I already pay for iCloud+ and it allows custom domains, so let the migration begin!
